    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Real-time Physics For Maya 2020</h2><br>Animate like it's 1999, or leverage full-body dynamics to automate the vast majority of overlapping animation that even respond to changes in environment and interacts with other characters.<br><br>Ragdoll enables animators to work directly with live physics in their character rigs, at very little overhead and tight integration with kinematics.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467930/extras/e379a7d40a236630e4977b3ae8cbfcdf.poster.avif?t=1609224981\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467930/extras/e379a7d40a236630e4977b3ae8cbfcdf.webm?t=1609224981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467930/extras/e379a7d40a236630e4977b3ae8cbfcdf.mp4?t=1609224981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can steer a simulated character with regular keyframe animation, like the above where the blue provides target poses and the colorful ragdoll obeys.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467930/extras/ae9b8fc9a9b9a2e8ba5f21f29a3b2c93.poster.avif?t=1609224981\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467930/extras/ae9b8fc9a9b9a2e8ba5f21f29a3b2c93.webm?t=1609224981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467930/extras/ae9b8fc9a9b9a2e8ba5f21f29a3b2c93.mp4?t=1609224981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The collision detection and constraints are stable and accurate enough to produce mathematical models, like this Reuleaux Triangle contraption.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467930/extras/ed14517b11e6f61017b84126b0930940.poster.avif?t=1609224981\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467930/extras/ed14517b11e6f61017b84126b0930940.webm?t=1609224981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467930/extras/ed14517b11e6f61017b84126b0930940.mp4?t=1609224981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can use it for cloth too, any overlapping animation will do just fine.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467930/extras/6b5ecca696f5940f22e392528cd711c5.poster.avif?t=1609224981\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467930/extras/6b5ecca696f5940f22e392528cd711c5.webm?t=1609224981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467930/extras/6b5ecca696f5940f22e392528cd711c5.mp4?t=1609224981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Including the kind of overlapping animation taking place internally, like muscles, fat and tendons.<br><br>I could go on, but you should really try it for yourself. Enjoy!",
